description: At half the size but with all the classic cashew taste you love, PLANTERS Salted Cashew Halves & Pieces are the ultimate in snack satisfaction. After more than a century of roasting, tweaking, and perfecting salty snacks, the makers of PLANTERS nuts know a thing or two about satisfying your cravings. These impressively creamy cashews are roasted to crunchy precision in peanut oil then seasoned with sea salt to create the savory flavor you know and love. A classic snack at parties, family game nights, and holiday get-togethers, these seasoned cashews are also delicious as snacks for road trips, lunch boxes, picnics, hikes or even at the office. Each 1oz Kosher serving of salted cashew halves contains 5 grams of plant-based protein and 160 calories to help curb your hunger and keep you going between meals. They come in a convenient 8oz airtight container with a resealable lid to keep them fresh and flavorful.
